<li id="cite_note-49"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-49">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r999302996"/><cite id="CITEREFHoelscher" class="citation journal cs1">Hoelscher, Stephen. "A Lost Work by Langston Hughes". <i>Smithsonian.com</i>. <b>50</b> (4): 20, 22–24.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Smithsonian.com&amp;rft.atitle=A+Lost+Work+by+Langston+Hughes&amp;rft.volume=50&amp;rft.issue=4&amp;rft.pages=20%2C+22-24&amp;rft.aulast=Hoelscher&amp;rft.aufirst=Stephen&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALangston+Hughes" class="Z3988"></span></span>
