<li id="cite_note-51"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-51">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">"The Negro Artist and the Racial Mountain"  (June 1926), <i><a href="/wiki/The_Nation" title="The Nation">The Nation</a></i>.</span>
